{"tid":636423,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"辯方：空姐死者未分手已與港龍機師約會","createTime":"2018-04-21T00:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T11:57:35.000Z","uid":72009,"like":154,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"7cb145e987150c34dd45ea533d5400c01d30fc66","tid":636423,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:10:01.000Z","msg":"被告莫俊賢聲稱得知前女友陳曼儀另結新歡，一時「火遮眼」殺人，證供陸續觸及二人感情瓜葛。死者胞妹指案發12月時死者已與被告分手，她印象中「大家姐好耐前已想分手，但分唔到」，「因為Oscar（被告洋名）不斷要求唔好分開」。惟辯方指，死者與被告拍拖數月後，不時與港龍機師約會出街。<br />\n死者胞妹表示，她見過被告不止一次，死者跟他於案發時已分手。此外，某天她在死者書枱找到一張定額罰款告票，屬於一名胡先生，後來知道胡是死者男友，但她不認識胡。<br />\n<br />\n友案發前與死者傾感情事<br />\n<br />\n控方另傳召死者好友，首先發現她失聯的港龍空少李浩境作供，兩人同期受訓，無所不談。李在2013年12月7日晚發現，Arbe（死者洋名） 的WhatsApp最後上線時間已是4日下午3時55分，他致電對方但電話不通，最終聯絡到死者胞妹，因而揭發案件。<br />\n辯方盤問時提到，死者在12月4日致電李傾談了一小時，因她與姓胡新男友剛剛拍拖一個月便發展得不太好，她更因此哭起來。李確認有此事，他指Arbe是一個大情大性的人，「佢可以因為好小事而喊，但喊完幾分鐘又好易𠱁番佢笑」。<br />\n辯方又指早於2013年1月，當Arbe與被告拍拖時，Arbe已與一名港龍機師約會出街，李當時不但知情，還警告過她要小心，因該名機師經常「媾女」。李指Arbe當時告訴他，與機師只是普通朋友，他當時提醒Arbe，「我想保護佢，避免佢再因感情受傷害」，因航空業界普遍認為機師屬於「成日換女朋友嘅人」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180421/20368306\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F20368306&d=f8R127f6THlCHb7JYRht2qWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=2b63c1aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180421%2F20368306&h=8b6ec064\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180421/20368306</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180421/large/a0301a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180421%2Flarge%2Fa0301a.gif&h=265a9cd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點夠機師鬥"},{"pid":"3511fa9d9e4822985484ef06023247708e649c9c","tid":636423,"uid":121473,"like":88,"dislike":3,"score":85,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:11:34.000Z","msg":"原來又係帽事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ac75c356594f0153ba94acb34dd8717fc8b7a5","tid":636423,"uid":3302,"like":117,"dislike":16,"score":101,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:16:57.000Z","msg":"港女=雞<br />\n仲要做飛雞<br />\n再加多十分"},{"pid":"f743f506711947ca475a86f46cdfc6d503dea984","tid":636423,"uid":7699,"like":50,"dislike":110,"score":-60,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:18:45.000Z","msg":"臭雞害左條仔一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"254a6c4ab909e0948edfcf072bb71bbcf2606c8d","tid":636423,"uid":66943,"like":16,"dislike":22,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:19:47.000Z","msg":"條臭雞把口應該好閪"},{"pid":"6d107e27a61ba4441401fb2887cbc5abec001257","tid":636423,"uid":125731,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:22:07.000Z","msg":"空少李浩境都想食佢咁款 ，做港女有幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"498c96f1996c2e24491191ec39db8a1d26723e09","tid":636423,"uid":91664,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:23:47.000Z","msg":"扯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b74243e8ecdbfe23445f79ca79e666f882ef7b49","tid":636423,"uid":18385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:26:05.000Z","msg":"唔記得呢單咩新聞了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a9fc7959e47cdfaeb9b0b9061585e0ba82bfac6","tid":636423,"uid":16256,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6d107e27a61ba4441401fb2887cbc5abec001257","tid":636423,"uid":125731,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:22:07.000Z","msg":"空少李浩境都想食佢咁款 ，做港女有幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T00:33:25.000Z","msg":"Hehe"},{"pid":"2274215cf574cff75b69cb2f5f72604ee625c50b","tid":636423,"uid