gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點夠機師鬥</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d85f2b1dd78cbad88a621e3e376b59a128c2afee","tid":636423,"uid":177710,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T03:18:59.000Z","msg":"又係一隻大陸雞，講真要條女有幾仆街先可以令一個人衝動殺左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"867da3b07e6575b6695ff2612f3bba468f7e0fce","tid":636423,"uid":7877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T03:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca0537a389924c7c7c14fb81db1fd53cdbb1459","tid":636423,"uid":112128,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T03:54:11.000Z","msg":"就算係事實都唔係減刑理由啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n就算結咗婚最多咪離婚，更何況只係男女朋友，係而家嘅社會派帽好常見，咁就要殺人分分鐘一日一百單殺人案"},{"pid":"1c144eef8b9575d9308a84494ca5def5ddb5883c","tid":636423,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T03:54:58.000Z","msg":"因龍"},{"pid":"57f492b7846f1d3c7799c5f728e36b4d8cf0f3c1","tid":636423,"uid":67500,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:08:47.000Z","msg":"女人咪一樣會出軌，成日話男人，賤女人"},{"pid":"1b085214e3449135488f945ca6a3da810fc5b651","tid":636423,"uid":41818,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:22:16.000Z","msg":"又係雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5820740610e265e5635de5859b09ed03317a04b6","tid":636423,"uid":52881,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T04:26:10.000Z","msg":"因果報應<br />\n<br />\n不過無論呢D新聞令人知道派帽可以死人都好，要派帽嘅都係一樣唔會顧人感受"},{"pid":"b8acd18a1c97cdb88634c02f1e09784d00180f91","tid":636423,"uid":40932,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"1eb150377acefbc42b75b8c6c97b35a2f6835675","tid":636423,"uid":37299,"like":22,"dislike":53,"score":-31,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T01:41:37.000Z","msg":"上面班友都癡撚線